description: Step into a world of refined sophistication at 26214 Kingsgate Lane, a meticulously reimagined estate in the gated community of Woodcreek Reserve, zoned to top-rated Katy ISD. Built by custom home builder Statley Homes, this 1.5-story residence offers 4 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, and a whole-home generator for peace of mind. Recently refreshed with new paint, updated fixtures, and energy-efficient windows installed in 2024, it’s truly move-in ready. The open-concept design invites effortless entertaining with a gourmet kitchen featuring rich cabinetry and granite countertops, flowing seamlessly into a family room with a cozy fireplace and views of your private backyard retreat. The primary suite impresses with soaring ceilings, abundant light, and a spa-inspired bath complete with a walk-in shower and jetted tub. Every detail blends comfort, efficiency, and timeless elegance—making this home a rare find.
